Name: Puzzles with cats
About the game: Hey! Have you already heard about the new game ' Puzzles with cats '? Puzzles with cats is a very interesting game, in each level you have to collect a super cute picture with a cat! Well, I invite you to quickly fold the picture in order to see the result and quickly proceed to the rest of the puzzles. Have a good game!
